jl7NhMmWwC&pg=PA428&dq=%22prix+de+rome%22+belgium&as_brr=3&ei=J4TlSfpUj5oyq5rVug0#PPA2,M1|accessdate=15 April 2009|year=1996|publisher=Harvard University Press|isbn=978-0-674-37299-3 |page=496}}</ref> *1891: [[Charles-Antoine Smulders]], music<ref name=Smulders>{{cite book|last1=Bergmans|first1=Charles|title=La Musique Et Les Musiciens|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OZI850DzpzUC&pg=PA150&dq=belgique+prix-de-rome&as_brr=3&ei=ILvlSbvwGImmNtOc_akN#PPA103,M1|accessdate=15 April 2009|year=2008|publisher=BiblioBazaar LLC|language=French|isbn=978-0-559-74298-9 |page=144}}</ref> *1893: [[Joseph Vander Meulen]], music<ref>{{cite book|last1=Bergmans|first1=Charles|title=La Musique Et Les Musiciens|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OZI850DzpzUC&pg=PA150&dq=belgique+prix-de-rome&as_brr=3&ei=ILvlSbvwGImmNtOc_akN#PPA103,M1|accessdate=15 April 2009|year=2008|publisher=BiblioBazaar LLC|language=French|isbn=978-0-559-74298-9|page=148}}</ref> *1895: [[Nicolas Daneau]], music<ref>{{cite book|last1=Bergmans|first1=Charles|title=La Musique Et Les Musiciens|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OZI850DzpzUC&pg=PA150&dq=belgique+prix-de-rome&as_brr=3&ei=ILvlSbvwGImmNtOc_akN#PPA103,M1|accessdate=15 April 2009 |year=2008|publisher=BiblioBazaar LLC|language=French|isbn=978-0-559-74298-9|page=146}}</ref> *1899: [[Léon Henry]], music<ref name=Rasse/> *1899: [[Albert Dupuis]], music<ref name=Rasse/> *1904: [[Joe English (painter)|Joe English]], painting<ref name=English>{{cite web|title=Drie tentoonstellingen Joe English|url=http://focus-wtv-kw.rnews.be/nl/regio/wvl-8600/drie-tentoonstellingen-joe-english/Article-1184684124786-1194458447042.html?params=forcelogo:wtv.be |publisher=Focus - WTV|language=Dutch|accessdate=16 April 2009}}</ref> *1907: [[Joe English (painter)|Joe English]], painting<ref name=English/> *1913: [[Alphonse Decuyper]], second prize *1919: [[René Barbier]], music *1922: [[Jean Absil]], music<ref>{{cite book|last1=Randel|first1=Don Michael|title=The Harvard biogra